            window.hs_config.gulpRGBA = (p1) => {\r\n
  const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
  const hex = options[0].toString()\r\n
  const transparent = options[1].toString()\r\n
  var c;\r\n
  if(/^#([A-Fa-f0-9]{3}){1,2}$/.test(hex)){\r\n
    c= hex.substring(1).split('');\r\n
    if(c.length== 3){\r\n
      c= [c[0], c[0], c[1], c[1], c[2], c[2]];\r\n
    }\r\n
    c= '0x'+c.join('');\r\n
    return 'rgba('+[(c>>16)&255, (c>>8)&255, c&255].join(',')+',' + transparent + ')';\r\n
  }\r\n
  throw new Error('Bad Hex');\r\n
}\r\n

                      window.hs_config.gulpRGBA = (p1) => {\r\n
            const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
            const hex = options[0].toString()\r\n
            const transparent = options[1].toString()\r\n
            var c;\r\n
            if(/^#([A-Fa-f0-9]{3}){1,2}$/.test(hex)){\r\n
              c= hex.substring(1).split('');\r\n
              if(c.length== 3){\r\n
                c= [c[0], c[0], c[1], c[1], c[2], c[2]];\r\n
              }\r\n
              c= '0x'+c.join('');\r\n
              return 'rgba('+[(c>>16)&255, (c>>8)&255, c&255].join(',')+',' + transparent + ')';\r\n
            }\r\n
            throw new Error('Bad Hex');\r\n
          }\r\n

            var usePound = false\r\n
            if (col[0] == "#") {\r\n

              usePound = true\r\n
            }\r\n
            var num = parseInt(col, 16)\r\n

                      window.hs_config.gulpRGBA = (p1) => {\r\n
            const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
            const hex = options[0].toString()\r\n
            const transparent = options[1].toString()\r\n
            var c;\r\n
            if(/^#([A-Fa-f0-9]{3}){1,2}$/.test(hex)){\r\n
              c= hex.substring(1).split('');\r\n
              if(c.length== 3){\r\n
                c= [c[0], c[0], c[1], c[1], c[2], c[2]];\r\n
              }\r\n
              c= '0x'+c.join('');\r\n
              return 'rgba('+[(c>>16)&255, (c>>8)&255, c&255].join(',')+',' + transparent + ')';\r\n
            }\r\n
            throw new Error('Bad Hex');\r\n
          }\r\n

            const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
            let col = options[0].toString()\r\n

            var usePound = false\r\n
            if (col[0] == "#") {\r\n
              col = col.slice(1)\r\n
              usePound = true\r\n
            }\r\n
            var num = parseInt(col, 16)\r\n
            var r = (num >> 16) + amt\r\n
            if (r > 255) {\r\n

                      window.hs_config.gulpRGBA = (p1) => {\r\n
            const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
            const hex = options[0].toString()\r\n
            const transparent = options[1].toString()\r\n
            var c;\r\n
            if(/^#([A-Fa-f0-9]{3}){1,2}$/.test(hex)){\r\n
              c= hex.substring(1).split('');\r\n
              if(c.length== 3){\r\n
                c= [c[0], c[0], c[1], c[1], c[2], c[2]];\r\n
              }\r\n
              c= '0x'+c.join('');\r\n
              return 'rgba('+[(c>>16)&255, (c>>8)&255, c&255].join(',')+',' + transparent + ')';\r\n
            }\r\n
            throw new Error('Bad Hex');\r\n
          }\r\n
                      window.hs_config.gulpDarken = (p1) => {\r\n
            const options = p1.split(',')\r\n
            let col = options[0].toString()\r\n
            let amt = -parseInt(options[1])\r\n
            var usePound = false\r\n
            if (col[0] == "#") {\r\n
              col = col.slice(1)\r\n
              usePound = true\r\n
            }\r\n
            var num = parseInt(col, 16)\r\n
            var r = (num >> 16) + amt\r\n
            if (r > 255) {\r\n
              r = 255\r\n
            } else if (r < 0) {\r\n
              r = 0\r\n
            }\r\n
            var b = ((num >> 8) & 0x00FF) + amt\r\n
            if (b > 255) {\r\n
              b = 255\r\n
            } else if (b < 0) {\r\n
              b = 0\r\n
            }\r\n
            var g = (num & 0x0000FF) + amt\r\n
            if (g > 255) {\r\n
              g = 255\r\n
            } else if (g < 0) {\r\n
              g = 0\r\n
            }\r\n
            return (usePound ? "#" : "") + (g | (b << 8) | (r << 16)).toString(16)\r\n
